#### Command

[replacement]
:%s/src/target/c (confirm)
:%s/src/target/g (global)

[undo]
u

[redo]
ctrl + R

[comment]
Visual Block (Shift + V)
:
:'<, '> (auto)
:'<, '> norm i // (or #)

[uncomment]
Visual Block (Shift + V)
:
:'<, '> (auto)
:'<, '> norm 2# (#: 1 for //, 2 for #, # means the the number of character to be removed)

[copy multi-line(#,#) to buffer]
:#,#/y

[paste buffer to the next of the specific line(#)]
:#pu

